Class NotationQueue<T>

java.lang.Object
NotationQueue<T>
Type Parameters:
T -
All Implemented Interfaces:
QueueInterface<T>
public class NotationQueue<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements QueueInterface<T>
The purpose of this class is to represent a queue of objects. This queue will primarily be used to store postfix expressions
Author:
Nicholas A. Baker
